metadata.name: BEGET
metadata.description:
[ X-ORCSTNS ]

[ 01: BEGET ]

Life grows in a replete kitchen. 
Mother life resists in a messy house.
Food less of nutrients that we are ingesting.
A garden to start all over again. 

[Improvised dance registered on march 2022, in a real house full of things] 

. . .

Dance, interpretation and creation by Ailo
Musical base and live direction by UntitledBPM
Musical arrangements, voices and SFX by Ailo
Food art and assistance by Luichi
Camera assistance by Guiye
